						               													<description>Description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Become the legend you are destined to be in the adventure card game of a lifetime.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Life &amp;amp; Legend is a deceptively complex game about risk, sacrifice, and the passage of time. You and your opponents explore a vast world seeking to make your wanderers legendary. In the world, they will have trouble, and their success depends on how well you manage their most valuable resource--Life.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As the world is experienced, the end draws closer. Decisions become agonizing. Missteps costly. Victories sweeter. Who will have led their wanderer to glory, when the road is at its end?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;FEATURES&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Playtime: 30+  minutes (playtime varies with different game modes)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1-4 players, ages 14+, including Solo AI Opponents!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Variant game modes for Solitaire play, Co-op, and Competitive Multiplayer!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;OVERVIEW&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Using 10 mystical Life Words, create dozens of character backgrounds, and ability combinations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Difficult decisions. Your choices have major impact from the beginning.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Take the quick and deadly path, or patiently bide your time. Press your luck, or be the master of your own fate.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Twist the World to your will as you discover powerful effect combinations your opponents never considered.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Life &amp;amp; Legend will provide hours of fun to any group of bold adventures seeking to become legendary.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
